Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.96,0:24:59.96,Spica - Title,,0,0,0,,Asumi's Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.46,0:01:57.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Our country's first manned exploratory space rocket, the Lion, was launched.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.39,0:02:04.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,However, 72 seconds after liftoff…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:07.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the liquid fuel booster suddenly exploded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.15,0:02:12.86,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And although the Space Control Center activated what could be called its self-destruct system…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.86,0:02:16.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the flight suspension system did not function correctly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:24.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The Lion fell into an urban area and caused a huge disaster with many civilian casualties.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Five years later…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.63,0:02:43.47,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey. I heard that Kamogawa's wife died.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:46.14,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. They said that the funeral is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:49.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She had been in that state for quite a while, hadn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:50.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.61,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Oh my, so that means it's just father and child?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:57.65,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan just entered elementary school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:03:00.70,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,How sad for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.90,0:03:35.86,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:38.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.74,0:03:48.12,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I'm Suzunari, Asumi-chan's teacher at Yuigahama Elementary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My condolences on your recent loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.50,0:03:53.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Um, is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.58,0:03:56.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sensei, have you seen Asumi around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.09,0:03:57.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:04:00.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Has something happened to Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:01.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:04.09,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…she took the cremated ashes and went off somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:05.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can't see it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.48,0:04:56.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey mister, what's your job?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:00.02,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,An advertising mascot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Or maybe someone from the circus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.11,0:05:06.07,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You… You can tell who I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.70,0:05:09.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I don't know, so that's why I'm asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:10.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Now this is surprising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:13.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can see me, little one?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is it strange for me to see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:18.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I am a ghost, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.96,0:05:22.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.63,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What a strange old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:24.84,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Besides, don't call me old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.30,0:05:29.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Even if I look like this, I'm still young and strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:32.10,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This T-shirt shows my fashion sense, you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.56,0:05:33.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:37.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you wearing that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,There are a lot of reasons behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.52,0:05:40.81,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:41.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:44.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, what is that box that you're carrying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:47.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This? Well you see…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:48.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.70,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.16,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So this is where you went.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's Suzunari-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.38,0:06:01.84,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your father is looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.00,0:06:03.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.18,0:06:10.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, will you be here tomorrow too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:10.93,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Great! Bye-bye, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.56,0:06:15.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:16.43,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:19.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't ask for your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.06,0:06:21.36,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My name? Let's see…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.86,0:06:23.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can just call me Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.52,0:06:26.78,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Lion-san? What a weird name!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.24,0:06:28.28,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:33.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Wa… Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.50,0:06:39.29,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Who was she talking with?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:49.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan, were you with someone back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.55,0:06:51.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:53.22,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He had a strange-looking lion head!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He said he was a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:58.31,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion? A ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:02.65,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Sometimes I just can't seem to keep up with this girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.20,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Suzunari-sensei, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:26.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Truly, my condolences on your recent loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:30.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for causing so much trouble today, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:34.26,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, Asumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I told you that this was something very important, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.35,0:07:43.31,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,These ashes aren't a toy to be played with!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.10,0:07:47.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you listening, Asumi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.99,0:07:50.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.58,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I guess being a single father is just no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.54,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She doesn't listen to a thing I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.54,0:08:00.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's not…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.87,0:08:03.42,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She may not truly feel that her mother has passed away…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:08.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…because when Asumi became old enough to be aware of things…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.13,0:08:10.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…my wife was already in that state.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I had to raise my daughter without her knowing her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.76,0:08:17.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. It's rude of me to ask…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.05,0:08:18.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…but what kind of person was your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.10,0:08:21.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you remember it as well, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:25.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The rocket explosion incident five years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My wife was a victim of that incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:32.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi was still only one year old.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:39.12,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,My wife received grave wounds on her face and head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:45.12,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,In the end, she passed away without regaining consciousness even once in those five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.46,0:08:50.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi once said that she'd like to be able to see her mother just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,That was last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:56.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After all, she had never seen her mother's face, except in pictures.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.39,0:08:58.76,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,But ever since that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:01.97,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi hasn't spoken once about her mother again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.35,0:09:04.27,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,At that time…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:08.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…what Asumi was thinking, how she felt…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:11.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.90,0:09:17.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So all that has happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.41,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:32.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Your mother became a star too, didn't she, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:34.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A star?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.76,0:09:37.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. That's what I think happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.44,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A star, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:06.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, you came to see me again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What about school?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.50,0:10:10.38,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's summer vacation right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.38,0:10:11.46,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:14.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You seem to have a lot of free time yourself, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.09,0:10:17.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is school fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.64,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.43,0:10:23.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Is Suzunari-sensei nice to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.18,0:10:27.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Lion-san, do you know Suzunari-sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:28.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,No, it's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.77,0:10:30.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I happened to see her yesterday, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:32.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sensei is very nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:35.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.11,0:10:37.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Sometimes she gets a lonely expression…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.78,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,A very lonely expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:51.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh my!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.38,0:11:00.80,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yuuko-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.09,0:11:03.60,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The stairs here are so long they really take their toll on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.72,0:11:07.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:16.53,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,My silly son must be pretty happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:18.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Every year at Obon…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.53,0:11:22.57,Spica - Notes,,0,0,0,,Note: Obon is an annual Buddhist ritual in July or August to honor the spirits of a family's ancestors.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:22.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…he has such a pretty woman come visit him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.57,0:11:23.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:30.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's right, today is the day of the Yuigahama fireworks display, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.25,0:11:34.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That boy wrote in a composition in elementary school…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:39.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…that his dream was to watch fireworks from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:42.51,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Afterward I heard from someone else that…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:46.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…fireworks are too small to be seen from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.18,0:11:48.06,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If you think about it, it's pretty obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.06,0:11:53.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But without even realizing that, that boy went on to be an astronaut…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:54.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He really was a silly boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.69,0:11:59.19,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's already been five years since then, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.11,0:12:06.20,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Shall we get going, Lion-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You'll help me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.37,0:12:11.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:24.68,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Already five years since then, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.69,0:12:43.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.49,0:12:49.53,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,This is a figure of the Lion's mascot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:51.79,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You can have it, Yuuko.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.79,0:12:55.42,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's just a little trinket they sell at the space center's gift shop, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.42,0:12:57.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What, just a trinket, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.54,0:12:58.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, now…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.17,0:13:02.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it'll make a good memento, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:04.34,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Don't be saying things like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.34,0:13:07.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,To someone who's going up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:10.72,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just kidding! I'm really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:13.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You really do get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:17.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just one week left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,It's pretty amazing…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.52,0:13:21.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The youngest astronaut ever…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:25.24,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yuuko…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.99,0:13:30.99,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After I get back from this flight safely…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.08,0:13:32.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.87,0:13:34.50,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Then, I'd like for us…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:36.50,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,For us?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:39.92,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, no, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:41.00,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:43.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Now you've got me wondering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.38,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,What is it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.84,0:13:47.30,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you after I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:48.55,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Say it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.55,0:13:50.18,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.64,0:13:52.60,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I'll make sure to tell you when I get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:54.60,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,No good, it has to be now!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Why in the world did I say that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:06.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A memento…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That was a pretty bad joke, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.62,0:14:17.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, Asumi-chan's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:25.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? Asumi-chan took the ashes and disappeared again!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:30.18,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hey, little one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.39,0:14:33.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.52,0:14:36.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm tired!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.77,0:14:39.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you're supposed to be younger than you look!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.48,0:14:40.73,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What a wimp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:45.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,These remains are as heavy as a person to my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:48.28,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Talking nonsense like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.28,0:14:50.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But do you want to rest for a while?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:52.37,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.99,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Could you play that thing from yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, gladly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.61,0:15:31.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, did you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.57,0:15:36.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Out of all the instruments…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.33,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…the harmonica was the first one to fly into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.00,0:15:41.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Space?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:47.38,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Yes. In 1965, the pilot of the American capsule, Gemini VI…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:50.84,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,…wore a 3cm wide harmonica around his neck when he went up into space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.34,0:15:55.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And then he sent a present of music down to Earth from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:59.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, you sure know a lot about space.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.47,0:16:00.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Have you ever been there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:03.85,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.85,0:16:08.65,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But the Earth must be really pretty when you see it from space.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:13.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'll never be able to see it since I ended up like this, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.45,0:16:17.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san, could you really be a ghost?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.16,0:16:20.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just once would have been fine, but I sure wanted to see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:26.21,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Asumi-chan! Answer me if you're there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.64,0:16:41.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Just a little further!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.83,0:17:06.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I knew it! There's a great view of it from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.51,0:17:14.47,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Ah, this is Suzunari.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.47,0:17:16.59,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,She doesn't seem to be out here by the shore either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:21.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I thought she might have come to the booths down here, so I asked around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:23.35,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,But no one said that they had seen Asumi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.98,0:17:27.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes. I'll look around here one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.65,0:17:28.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:45.00,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Mom will be happy now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.00,0:17:46.75,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm sure she will.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.75,0:17:47.62,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:48.29,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:52.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank you for helping me, Lion-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:56.80,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Little one, I have a favor to ask of you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Could I ask you for it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.55,0:18:00.05,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yeah! That's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.14,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Geez, where did you go, Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,He had a strange-looking lion head!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:14.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,This couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.78,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,A kidnapping?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.03,0:18:21.37,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Really… where could she have wandered off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.45,0:18:27.04,Spica - Italic,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should contact the police now…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.71,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.71,0:18:38.88,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,The door was locked, so I—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.68,0:18:44.51,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Do you understand why I hit you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.73,0:18:49.23,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I told you already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.15,0:18:53.19,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's not a toy, it's something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.27,0:18:57.32,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And yet you still keep running off with it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.78,0:18:59.15,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Those ashes are…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.45,0:19:03.95,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,They're the ashes of my mother who gave birth to me.{ffs}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.95,0:19:06.08,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,If you understand that, then why…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:08.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Where did you take them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.12,0:19:13.59,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,I buried them in the place with the prettiest view of the Yuigahama Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:14.96,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:17.59,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,She seemed so lonely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.67,0:19:26.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Closed up in that dark hospital room…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.77,0:19:30.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then she got put in a little box when she died…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I felt so sorry for Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.52,0:19:37.36,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You said it yourself, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.36,0:19:42.16,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,You said Mom always loved the Yuigahama Bay, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:45.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:52.58,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Well… was Mom…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.58,0:19:55.13,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…happy to see the ocean again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.72,0:20:08.01,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,These stairs are so long, geez!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:13.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.10,0:20:16.56,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What? You found her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.56,0:20:18.57,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,You found Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:20.82,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.61,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I'm very sorry to have worried you, sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.61,0:20:27.16,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Oh, and Asumi said that she had something to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:29.91,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hello, sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.87,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.87,0:20:33.21,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,What is it, this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.04,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Sensei, do you know Lion-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:40.76,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san said that he had something he wanted me to tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:43.13,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Hold on, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.55,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Okay, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:49.26,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,“Don't be too mean to the Lion doll, Yuuko.”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:52.98,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Umm…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:54.44,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,See ya, sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.44,0:20:56.06,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hold on! Asumi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:02.11,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,He's the only one who knows about this doll.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:32.97,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Yuuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:36.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Takano-kun…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:05.72,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,After I get back from this flight safely, I'd like for us…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.34,0:22:09.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.31,0:22:18.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,That's mean, going and becoming a star by yourself…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.61,0:22:22.77,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Takano-kun, that's mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.28,0:22:31.87,Spica - Offscreen,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:34.54,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.50,0:22:37.66,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Maybe he's not here today…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.71,0:22:42.04,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Hey, you fly to space on a rocket, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:46.30,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm going to be a rocket driver!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.59,0:22:49.43,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Then I'll let you ride for free, Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.97,0:22:53.18,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,So let me hear lots more stories!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.85,0:22:55.52,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Lion-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.31,0:24:35.94,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Winter of the third year of middle school…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.94,0:24:38.48,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,We have to be deciding our futures now…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.48,0:24:40.49,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…but I'm still not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.49,0:24:42.74,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,I want to attend Tokyo Space University…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.74,0:24:45.03,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…and learn to be an astronaut…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.03,0:24:47.45,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,…but I'm sure that my dad will be against it…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.45,0:24:53.17,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,And it takes lots of money, so I think that maybe I should give up on that dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.75,0:24:57.25,Spica - Main,,0,0,0,,Next time on Twin Spica: Asumi's Dream.